  "coverage": "Found 4 finished group-stage matches across June 11-12. June 11 (Group A): Mexico 2-0 South Africa; South Korea 2-1 Czech Republic. June 12: Canada 1-1 Bosnia and Herzegovina (Group B); United States 3-0 Paraguay (Group D). The USA-Paraguay final (3-0) was verified directly on the ESPN match page as FT to avoid reporting the 3-0 halftime score by coincidence; one early search incorrectly suggested 0-1, which was contradicted by FIFA, ESPN, Yahoo, and NBC. June 13 matches (Qatar-Switzerland Group B, Brazil-Morocco Group C, Haiti-Scotland Group C, Australia-Turkey Group D) had NOT finished yet as of the latest available data — all were still scheduled to kick off later on June 13, so none are included. Stale ESPN/cached pages were cross-checked against Sofascore, olympics.com live-results, SBS, and FIFA to confirm no June 13 results exist yet. All scores reflect full-time results."
